        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Accountability for Endless Wars Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill provides for the automatic termination of laws that authorize the use of military force or declare war.</p> <p>Any such existing law terminates six months after this bill's enactment; any such future law terminates 10 years after enactment.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
